A demo springboot app for task manager.
Moving towards MVC architecture.
following single responsibility.
defining ErrorHandling class in the service file. ( only 1 service file, else its good practice to create diff errorHandling file)

Made DTO and used them for create , update and response body.
Made Mapper func for DTO.
Made Service for functional logic.


